560
00:53:14,224 --> 00:53:18,172
The gun only knows how to avenge...

561
00:53:19,563 --> 00:53:21,065
Commander...

562
00:53:21,498 --> 00:53:26,311
revenge does not set you free..

563
00:53:26,370 --> 00:53:31,342
True freedom lies beyond violence“.

564
00:53:33,544 --> 00:53:39,495
