566
00:53:51,095 --> 00:53:52,768
I am not going anywhere.

567
00:53:53,030 --> 00:53:54,532
I am staying here.

568
00:53:58,402 --> 00:54:00,279
With my father.

569
00:54:12,983 --> 00:54:14,621
Jahid.. to the left...

570
00:54:25,429 --> 00:54:26,533
What is it now?

571
00:54:26,630 --> 00:54:28,667
