shot yourself that day?

583
00:55:04,201 --> 00:55:05,680
Do you doubt me?

584
00:55:07,471 --> 00:55:09,417
No. I'm sure.

585
00:55:10,974 --> 00:55:12,681
You wouldn't have.

586
00:55:18,582 --> 00:55:22,223
Was there any other reason
for me to live... besides you?

587
00:55:27,124 --> 00:55:28,660
Or is there?

588
00:55:31,328 --> 00:55:36,300
