cared for me. Our marriage was dead.

592
00:55:50,247 --> 00:55:52,625
Which is why he gambled his life...

593
00:55:53,117 --> 00:55:54,425
our home...

594
00:55:55,185 --> 00:55:57,165
our honor...

595
00:55:57,221 --> 00:56:00,725
your future... risked it all.

596
00:56:03,661 --> 00:56:10,476
Do we have to see everything
through your eyes?

597
00:56:11,735 --> 00:56:13,009
Always?

598
00:56:14,972 --> 00:56:19,250
There are other ways of seeing.
Try sometime...

599
00:56:27,050 --> 00:56:30,520
Either way,
you will always blame me...

600
00:56:33,657 --> 00:56:37,662
I am used to it.

601
00:56:43,400 --> 00:56:47,507
I know you love your father
more than anyone else...

602
00:56:51,175 --> 00:56:53,348
You certainly don't realise...

603
00:56:55,079 --> 00:56:57,753
What I went through
when you were away.

604
00:56:59,249 --> 00:57:05,097
