it'll happen again.

652
01:01:03,560 --> 01:01:07,007
Does the law allow you to torture
people you've arrested?

653
01:01:07,064 --> 01:01:09,305
The Indian army is one of the most...

654
01:01:09,366 --> 01:01:11,744
