736
01:09:49,752 --> 01:09:51,060
In a faraway place...

737
01:09:52,522 --> 01:09:54,433
Very far...

738
01:09:56,092 --> 01:09:59,005
You said you had
a message from him...

739
01:09:59,062 --> 01:10:00,837
Yes.

740
01:10:01,598 --> 01:10:02,804
