787
01:13:41,884 --> 01:13:45,889
We bore our torments together
in the same cell.

788
01:13:46,589 --> 01:13:48,694
We were chained together.

789
01:13:50,760 --> 01:13:54,105
It seems we will be
killed together as well.

790
01:13:55,498 --> 01:13:58,570
You can die doctor, but I won't.

791
01:14:00,970 --> 01:14:02,381
And how is that?

792
01:14:02,939 --> 01:14:05,852
You are the body
and I'm the soul...

793
01:14:05,909 --> 01:14:08,515
You are mortal and I'm immortal!

794
01:14:11,914 --> 01:14:14,793
