795
01:14:16,452 --> 01:14:19,365
I am the river and the tree...

796
01:14:19,889 --> 01:14:22,699
The Jhelum and the Chinar...

797
01:14:24,060 --> 01:14:26,870
I'm both..
a temple and a mosque...

798
01:14:27,597 --> 01:14:30,100
A Shia and a Sunni, I'm both.

799
01:14:31,634 --> 01:14:33,409
A Hindu as well.

800
01:14:35,104 --> 01:14:37,846
I always was... I am...

801
01:14:38,808 --> 01:14:40,754
I will always be...

