803
01:14:48,951 --> 01:14:52,057
Strange camps... stranger names...

804
01:14:54,357 --> 01:14:57,361
Bo-Bo land, Hotel 6...

805
01:14:57,527 --> 01:14:58,767
Faraz cinema...

806
01:15:41,971 --> 01:15:46,852
